Tefft Johnson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tefft_Johnson 0 William Tefft Johnson, Jr. (September 23, 1883 – October 15, 1956), better known as Tefft Johnson, was an American stage and film actor, and film director and screenwriter. He appeared in 131 films between 1909 and 1926.
